Package com.example.wizard_project.Classes

Class Facility

java.lang.Object
com.example.wizard_project.Classes.Facility
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Facility extends Object implements Serializable
The Facility class represents a facility in the application, and provides methods to manage facility data. This class is designed to interact with Firestore to store and retrieve facility data.
